    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and looks stunning, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
