      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, retaining its original deep-gloss luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. The interior is indistinguishable from new, featuring supple, uncreased leather, pristine door sills, and that distinct factory-fresh aroma. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete, organized history file included. From the immaculate undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in premium rubber, this vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of its model. It drives with the tight, responsive precision of a brand-new machine. No scratches, no imperfections, and zero compromises\u2014this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for.",
